information presented on this site is for general use only and is not intended
to provide personal medical advice or substitute for the advice of your
physician. If you have questions or concerns about individual health matters
or the management of your diabetes, please consult your diabetes care team.
Products highlighted on the Diabetes UK website are not necessarily endorsed
